00:26:39.330 --> 00:26:40.830
1999

00:26:40.830 --> 00:26:41.430
Why?

00:26:41.430 --> 00:26:42.330
Because now

00:26:42.330 --> 00:26:43.830
There either needs to be a messenger

00:26:43.830 --> 00:26:45.230
Or there needs to be doom

00:26:45.230 --> 00:26:46.630
So because there's no messenger

00:26:46.630 --> 00:26:47.530
There's going to be doom

00:26:47.530 --> 00:26:48.430
And guess what?

00:26:48.430 --> 00:26:50.530
We saw the 1st of January 2000

00:26:50.530 --> 00:26:51.730
Mashallah

00:26:51.730 --> 00:26:53.530
So some way down the line they went wrong

00:26:53.530 --> 00:26:55.630
There was a messenger who came a long long time ago

00:26:55.630 --> 00:26:57.730
We don't believe that as Muslims

00:26:57.730 --> 00:26:59.630
But it's interesting to see how

00:26:59.630 --> 00:27:01.930
Now suddenly they're very quiet about it

00:27:01.930 --> 00:27:04.230
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us goodness

00:27:04.230 --> 00:27:06.030
It's like some people from amongst us

00:27:06.030 --> 00:27:07.930
They say the Mahdi was born 40 years ago

00:27:07.930 --> 00:27:09.930
And the Mahdi was born so many years ago

00:27:09.930 --> 00:27:11.530
He's going to come out in 1993

00:27:11.530 --> 00:27:13.030
People look for him, he didn't come

00:27:13.030 --> 00:27:14.230
Coming out in 1999

00:27:14.230 --> 00:27:15.530
They look for him, he didn't come

00:27:15.530 --> 00:27:17.330
20,000 meaning 2000

00:27:17.330 --> 00:27:18.330
No, he didn't come

00:27:18.330 --> 00:27:20.530
And then 2005 he didn't come

00:27:20.530 --> 00:27:22.030
Now they're saying 2012

00:27:22.030 --> 00:27:23.730
Allah knows best

00:27:23.730 --> 00:27:25.630
But all this is just something

00:27:25.630 --> 00:27:27.530
Which people are guessing and trying

00:27:27.530 --> 00:27:29.430
If the Prophet salallahu alaihi wasallam

00:27:29.430 --> 00:27:31.830
Could not pinpoint when the Mahdi is coming

00:27:31.830 --> 00:27:34.130
Who are we to be able to suddenly pinpoint

00:27:34.130 --> 00:27:36.330
When he's going to come?

00:27:36.330 --> 00:27:38.830
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala help us prepare

00:27:38.830 --> 00:27:41.630
Rather than just blow our trumpet about things

00:27:41.630 --> 00:27:43.230
That are perhaps, you know, coming

00:27:43.230 --> 00:27:45.430
But to try and pinpoint

00:27:45.430 --> 00:27:46.830
When exactly they're happening

00:27:46.830 --> 00:27:48.230
We will probably lose focus

00:27:48.230 --> 00:27:49.930
As to what we're supposed to be doing

00:27:49.930 --> 00:27:51.930
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala bless us all

00:27:51.930 --> 00:27:54.630
So Isa alaihi salam makes mention of it

00:27:54.630 --> 00:27:56.030
Ibrahim alaihi salatu wassalam

00:27:56.030 --> 00:27:56.930
Makes mention of it

00:27:56.930 --> 00:27:59.630
And we made mention of how it is also

00:27:59.630 --> 00:28:01.730
In the Bible and the Torah

00:28:01.730 --> 00:28:03.830
And if you look at the people at the time

00:28:03.830 --> 00:28:05.930
What had happened, very interesting

00:28:05.930 --> 00:28:07.530
The Jews had already been told

00:28:07.530 --> 00:28:10.330
There is a man who's going to be sent in Arabia

00:28:10.330 --> 00:28:11.830
Between two deserts

00:28:11.830 --> 00:28:13.530
Where there are date palms

00:28:13.530 --> 00:28:14.630
Between two deserts

00:28:14.630 --> 00:28:15.630
Where there are date palms

00:28:15.630 --> 00:28:17.730
That is where he will finally end up

00:28:17.730 --> 00:28:19.630
He's going to migrate to that area

00:28:19.630 --> 00:28:20.730
Now if you were told

00:28:20.730 --> 00:28:22.230
Someone is coming in Arabia

00:28:22.230 --> 00:28:25.230
Well, Arabia extends from far east to west

00:28:25.230 --> 00:28:27.630
To north to south, large land

00:28:27.630 --> 00:28:28.530
Where are you going to go?

00:28:28.530 --> 00:28:29.930
You won't know

00:28:29.930 --> 00:28:31.130
But if someone told you

00:28:31.130 --> 00:28:33.830
Ultimately he's going to migrate to a place

00:28:33.830 --> 00:28:36.530
Which has date palms between two deserts

00:28:36.530 --> 00:28:38.030
You can go to one of two areas

00:28:38.030 --> 00:28:39.230
Either to Tabuk

00:28:39.230 --> 00:28:41.830
Or either you can go to

00:28:41.830 --> 00:28:43.130
Madinah Munawwarah

00:28:43.130 --> 00:28:45.030
Because Madinah Munawwarah subhanallah

00:28:45.030 --> 00:28:47.530
There are date palms between the deserts

00:28:47.530 --> 00:28:50.530
And if you take a look at Tabuk in that area

00:28:50.630 --> 00:28:52.530
In fact, Khyber, not Tabuk

00:28:52.530 --> 00:28:53.830
The area near Khyber

00:28:53.830 --> 00:28:56.030
You will find something quite similar as well

00:28:56.030 --> 00:28:57.930
Not very far off from Madinah Munawwarah

00:28:57.930 --> 00:28:59.930
We ask Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala to bless us

00:28:59.930 --> 00:29:00.930
So what they did?

00:29:00.930 --> 00:29:03.030
They started descending south

00:29:03.030 --> 00:29:05.430
From where they were in the north, in Sham

00:29:05.430 --> 00:29:06.630
And they began to come

00:29:06.630 --> 00:29:07.430
To do what?

00:29:07.430 --> 00:29:09.430
To prepare to meet this messenger

00:29:09.430 --> 00:29:10.630
According to their books

00:29:10.630 --> 00:29:14.430
This is why the Jewish clan settled around Madinah Munawwarah

00:29:14.430 --> 00:29:16.230
For your information, where did they come from?

00:29:16.230 --> 00:29:17.530
They came from further up north

00:29:17.530 --> 00:29:18.430
Why did they come?

00:29:18.430 --> 00:29:21.230
They came to welcome this messenger

00:29:21.230 --> 00:29:24.230
But they did not expect him not to be from amongst them

00:29:24.230 --> 00:29:26.230
Because they were used to all the messengers

00:29:26.230 --> 00:29:27.730
Being from the children of his haq

00:29:27.730 --> 00:29:29.330
This is what it was

00:29:29.330 --> 00:29:30.430
Allahu Akbar

00:29:30.430 --> 00:29:32.630
So you look at Banu al-Nadheer, Banu Qaynuqaa

00:29:32.630 --> 00:29:34.330
They had from amongst them the leaders

00:29:34.330 --> 00:29:35.930
Those who were very pious

00:29:35.930 --> 00:29:38.730
Those who knew the Torah inside out

00:29:38.730 --> 00:29:39.930
Those who told their people

00:29:39.930 --> 00:29:41.230
People are coming here

00:29:41.230 --> 00:29:44.630
In fact, the Ansar, do you know what they say?

00:29:44.630 --> 00:29:47.130
They say that these Jewish people in Madinah Munawwarah

00:29:47.130 --> 00:29:50.230
They used to tell us the messenger is coming anytime now

00:29:50.230 --> 00:29:53.230
When he comes, we are going to be fighting you

00:29:53.230 --> 00:29:56.630
In the same way that Ad and Thamud were fought before

00:29:56.630 --> 00:29:59.830
And we will destroy you to bits and pieces with that messenger

00:29:59.830 --> 00:30:01.230
When he came, they rejected him

00:30:01.230 --> 00:30:03.230
Because he was from the cousin side

00:30:03.230 --> 00:30:04.330
Look at the racism

00:30:04.330 --> 00:30:05.330
Look at the tribalism

00:30:05.330 --> 00:30:08.330
Look at the oldest type of nepotism that took place

00:30:08.330 --> 00:30:10.830
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala protect us

00:30:10.830 --> 00:30:11.930
Allahu Akbar

00:30:11.930 --> 00:30:13.730
Remember, virtue is virtue

00:30:13.830 --> 00:30:17.130
If a man comes from far off

00:30:17.130 --> 00:30:19.030
Different race, different size

00:30:19.030 --> 00:30:22.630
Totally unacceptable in terms of financial level

00:30:22.630 --> 00:30:23.230
No problem

00:30:23.230 --> 00:30:25.230
For as long as his message is solid

00:30:25.230 --> 00:30:25.730
You take it

00:30:25.730 --> 00:30:27.430
Maybe Allah gave him something

00:30:27.430 --> 00:30:29.330
That he has not given in your children

00:30:29.330 --> 00:30:30.530
Or around you

00:30:30.530 --> 00:30:33.330
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala never make us from those

00:30:33.330 --> 00:30:35.530
Who lose opportunities when we have them

00:30:35.530 --> 00:30:36.430
You never know

00:30:36.430 --> 00:30:39.730
Who is going to have a message that will turn your whole life

00:30:39.730 --> 00:30:42.630
And that will bring you closer to Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:30:42.630 --> 00:30:44.230
So don't take things lightly

00:30:44.230 --> 00:30:45.030
Listen

00:30:45.030 --> 00:30:47.030
And this is why we need to attend the talks

00:30:47.030 --> 00:30:50.030
When people have talks in the masajid

00:30:50.030 --> 00:30:52.530
In our community we have ulama

00:30:52.530 --> 00:30:54.030
Who tirelessly work

00:30:54.030 --> 00:30:55.030
They have their lessons

00:30:55.030 --> 00:30:56.130
They have their ahadith

00:30:56.130 --> 00:30:58.430
They have their daily readings and so on

00:30:58.430 --> 00:30:59.530
Try to attend

00:30:59.530 --> 00:31:00.630
Try to make it a point

00:31:00.630 --> 00:31:02.830
You never know which five minutes of your time

00:31:02.830 --> 00:31:05.530
Could actually result in the changing of your whole life

00:31:05.530 --> 00:31:08.130
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala change our lives

00:31:08.130 --> 00:31:10.430
Towards positive

00:31:10.430 --> 00:31:13.030
So here the people had come to this area

00:31:13.030 --> 00:31:15.030
I want to make mention of a few incidents

00:31:15.030 --> 00:31:17.930
Because it's very important for us to know what had happened

00:31:17.930 --> 00:31:20.330
If you take a look at the people of the book

00:31:20.330 --> 00:31:20.930
They knew him

00:31:20.930 --> 00:31:22.130
Some of them accepted him

00:31:22.130 --> 00:31:24.930
When he came in as a nabi

00:31:24.930 --> 00:31:26.430
Some of them rejected him

00:31:26.430 --> 00:31:28.930
All those who rejected him only did it

00:31:28.930 --> 00:31:30.630
Because he was not from amongst them

00:31:30.630 --> 00:31:31.730
Nothing else

00:31:31.730 --> 00:31:32.530
It's not my son

00:31:32.530 --> 00:31:33.830
So I'm not reading behind that one

00:31:33.830 --> 00:31:34.730
Making noise

00:31:34.730 --> 00:31:36.030
But when your son reads

00:31:36.030 --> 00:31:37.130
Then everybody is going to be there

00:31:37.130 --> 00:31:38.430
Allahu akbar

00:31:38.430 --> 00:31:40.830
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala help us and guide us

00:31:40.830 --> 00:31:43.130
We don't want that ignorance in us

00:31:43.130 --> 00:31:45.630
We don't want the ignorance whereby we get jealous

00:31:45.630 --> 00:31:47.730
Because the deen is with someone else

00:31:47.730 --> 00:31:50.030
And the spreading of it is with someone else

00:31:50.030 --> 00:31:50.930
Make dua for them

00:31:50.930 --> 00:31:51.630
Learn from them

00:31:51.630 --> 00:31:52.730
Benefit from them

00:31:52.730 --> 00:31:57.030
And make dua that Allah granted to us in our offspring as well

00:31:57.030 --> 00:31:59.730
Let me give you the one story of a sahabi

00:31:59.730 --> 00:32:02.630
Known as Salamah Ibn Salamah radiallahu anhu

00:32:02.630 --> 00:32:05.830
He says we had a neighbor who was a Jewish man

00:32:05.830 --> 00:32:07.430
And one day he came out to us

00:32:07.430 --> 00:32:10.130
When we were sitting and he started telling us something

00:32:10.130 --> 00:32:10.830
What was he saying?

00:32:10.830 --> 00:32:14.230
Now remember these people were

00:32:14.230 --> 00:32:15.530
They used to worship idols

00:32:15.530 --> 00:32:18.130
Subhanallah, idol worshipers

00:32:18.130 --> 00:32:21.330
And this Jewish man was not an idol worshiper

00:32:21.330 --> 00:32:23.030
He used to worship Allah alone

00:32:23.030 --> 00:32:25.430
And he came out and what did he say?

00:32:25.430 --> 00:32:28.430
He said do you know there is life after death?

00:32:28.430 --> 00:32:30.630
Oh, the kuffar did not used to believe that

00:32:30.630 --> 00:32:31.830
Do you know there is heaven?

00:32:31.830 --> 00:32:32.530
There is hell

00:32:32.530 --> 00:32:34.730
Look the Jewish beliefs just like ours

00:32:34.730 --> 00:32:35.730
Do you know there is heaven?

00:32:35.730 --> 00:32:36.330
There is hell

00:32:36.330 --> 00:32:37.930
You are going to be resurrected

00:32:37.930 --> 00:32:40.630
You are going to be accountable for all your deeds

00:32:40.630 --> 00:32:42.130
And you will either go to heaven and hell

00:32:42.130 --> 00:32:43.430
They said hey, relax

00:32:43.430 --> 00:32:45.130
What are you talking about here?

00:32:45.130 --> 00:32:46.430
Can there be heaven?

00:32:46.430 --> 00:32:47.930
After we die there's going to be something

00:32:47.930 --> 00:32:49.230
You mean we're going to come back to life?

00:32:49.230 --> 00:32:50.230
He said yes

00:32:50.230 --> 00:32:51.530
What's the sign of it?

00:32:51.530 --> 00:32:53.130
They asked him

00:32:53.130 --> 00:32:55.930
So he says the sign of it is you know what?

00:32:55.930 --> 00:32:59.530
We're about to witness the coming of a messenger

00:32:59.530 --> 00:33:02.630
In this area anytime now

00:33:02.630 --> 00:33:05.330
So they said when will that be?

00:33:05.330 --> 00:33:09.430
So he looked at Salamah ibn Salamah radiallahu anhu

00:33:09.430 --> 00:33:11.030
He was the youngest from amongst them

00:33:11.030 --> 00:33:11.830
Young boy

00:33:11.830 --> 00:33:12.730
He looked at him and he says

00:33:12.730 --> 00:33:15.630
If this man is this boy's given life

00:33:15.630 --> 00:33:16.930
He will definitely see him

00:33:16.930 --> 00:33:18.230
Because we are already there

00:33:18.230 --> 00:33:19.330
The time has come

00:33:19.330 --> 00:33:21.730
It's reported that some days later

00:33:21.730 --> 00:33:23.730
Muhammad salallahu alayhi wasalam came

00:33:23.730 --> 00:33:24.330
Subhanallah

00:33:24.330 --> 00:33:25.830
Some days later

00:33:25.830 --> 00:33:27.030
Muhammad salallahu alayhi wasalam came

00:33:27.030 --> 00:33:28.130
And you know what?

00:33:28.130 --> 00:33:30.230
The same man did not accept

00:33:30.230 --> 00:33:31.030
So they all told him

00:33:31.030 --> 00:33:34.030
But weren't you the one telling us that someone will come

00:33:34.030 --> 00:33:37.430
He brought exactly the message you are saying now

00:33:37.430 --> 00:33:39.030
Meaning you just said

00:33:39.030 --> 00:33:40.830
He brought exactly that message

00:33:40.830 --> 00:33:41.730
Why don't you accept?

00:33:41.730 --> 00:33:42.730
He says no

00:33:42.730 --> 00:33:44.130
We're not going to accept him

00:33:44.130 --> 00:33:47.230
Because we didn't expect him to be from amongst you guys

00:33:47.230 --> 00:33:48.930
Allahu Akbar

00:33:48.930 --> 00:33:52.330
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala protect us from this

00:33:52.330 --> 00:33:53.830
Then we have another lesson

00:33:53.830 --> 00:33:55.330
Ka'bal ahbar

00:33:55.330 --> 00:33:57.730
He was a man

00:33:57.730 --> 00:34:00.830
Who did not accept Islam at the time of Muhammad salallahu alayhi wasalam

00:34:00.830 --> 00:34:02.830
But after the death of Muhammad salallahu alayhi wasalam

00:34:02.830 --> 00:34:05.830
It is reported that at the time of Abu Bakr as-Siddiq radiallahu anhu

00:34:05.830 --> 00:34:06.630
He accepted Islam

00:34:06.630 --> 00:34:10.130
So he's one of those who saw the messenger salallahu alayhi wasalam

00:34:10.130 --> 00:34:11.430
But he's not a sahabi

00:34:11.430 --> 00:34:13.330
Because he wasn't a mumin at that time

00:34:13.330 --> 00:34:14.830
He only accepted Islam

00:34:14.830 --> 00:34:16.830
After Muhammad salallahu alayhi wasalam

00:34:16.830 --> 00:34:17.630
Amazing

00:34:17.630 --> 00:34:18.630
So this Ka'bal ahbar

00:34:18.630 --> 00:34:19.630
Do you know what he says?

00:34:19.630 --> 00:34:20.330
A Jewish man

00:34:20.330 --> 00:34:23.730
He says the qualities of Muhammad salallahu alayhi wasalam

00:34:23.730 --> 00:34:27.730
Are mentioned in the Taurah

00:34:27.730 --> 00:34:32.430
Exactly how they are made mention of in the Quran

00:34:32.430 --> 00:34:34.430
And he says he is a messenger

00:34:34.430 --> 00:34:35.530
Who speaks well

00:34:35.530 --> 00:34:36.530
He doesn't lie

00:34:36.530 --> 00:34:37.630
He comes with goodness

00:34:37.630 --> 00:34:40.630
He doesn't eat any charities

00:34:40.630 --> 00:34:42.530
But he might eat from a gift

00:34:42.530 --> 00:34:45.230
And he is a person who is very eloquent

00:34:45.230 --> 00:34:45.930
Very calm

00:34:45.930 --> 00:34:46.630
Very clean

00:34:46.630 --> 00:34:47.630
He doesn't swear

00:34:47.630 --> 00:34:49.030
He doesn't cheat in business

00:34:49.030 --> 00:34:50.330
And he teaches goodness

00:34:50.330 --> 00:34:53.130
He only teaches that which is good and so on

00:34:53.130 --> 00:34:53.930
And you know what?

00:34:53.930 --> 00:34:55.030
When the teachings came

00:34:55.030 --> 00:34:56.830
He delayed in accepting the message

00:34:56.830 --> 00:34:58.530
Just Allah had blessed him

00:34:58.530 --> 00:35:01.430
That he had had life long enough to accept Islam

00:35:01.430 --> 00:35:03.430
But he was not written from amongst the sahaba

00:35:03.430 --> 00:35:04.430
Radhiallahu anhum

00:35:04.430 --> 00:35:06.230
As I explained a few moments ago

00:35:06.230 --> 00:35:07.430
Because he accepted Islam

00:35:07.430 --> 00:35:09.030
Only at the time of Abu Bakr

00:35:09.030 --> 00:35:10.730
Al-Siddiq radhiallahu anhum

00:35:10.730 --> 00:35:12.230
Then there is another incident

00:35:12.230 --> 00:35:14.130
That is mentioned in Sahih al-Bukhari

00:35:14.130 --> 00:35:16.630
Of Abdullah ibn Amr ibn Al-Asr radhiallahu anhum

00:35:16.630 --> 00:35:17.530
Who says

00:35:17.530 --> 00:35:18.230
When he was asked

00:35:18.230 --> 00:35:19.330
He says wallahi

00:35:19.330 --> 00:35:21.630
The qualities of Muhammad salallahu alayhi wasalam

00:35:21.630 --> 00:35:23.430
Have been mentioned in the Taurah

00:35:23.430 --> 00:35:26.130
Just like they are mentioned in the Quran

00:35:26.130 --> 00:35:27.630
And he read the verse

00:35:27.630 --> 00:35:30.130
O Prophet

00:35:30.130 --> 00:35:47.530
We have sent you as a witness, as a bearer of good news

00:35:47.530 --> 00:35:50.030
And as a warner at the same time

00:35:50.030 --> 00:35:53.630
And a caller who calls towards Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:35:53.630 --> 00:35:54.830
By his permission

00:35:54.830 --> 00:35:55.430
And so on

00:35:55.430 --> 00:35:57.230
The verse subhanallah

00:35:57.230 --> 00:36:00.330
So these qualities are mentioned in the Taurah

00:36:00.330 --> 00:36:03.430
And this is made mention of in Sahih al-Bukhari

00:36:03.430 --> 00:36:05.230
And what happened

00:36:05.230 --> 00:36:08.630
It is also made mention that the messenger will come

00:36:08.630 --> 00:36:09.930
Which messenger

00:36:09.930 --> 00:36:13.630
The one who will open the eyes that have been blind

00:36:13.630 --> 00:36:15.930
The one who will open the ears

00:36:15.930 --> 00:36:17.530
That would have been deaf

00:36:17.530 --> 00:36:21.630
The one whom Allah will open through the hearts

00:36:21.630 --> 00:36:22.230
That were blocked

00:36:22.230 --> 00:36:23.730
So it's Allah who does that

00:36:23.730 --> 00:36:26.630
But through the messenger salallahu alayhi wasalam

00:36:26.630 --> 00:36:27.630
Amazing

00:36:27.630 --> 00:36:28.830
Now what does this mean

00:36:28.830 --> 00:36:30.430
People have eyes we see

00:36:30.430 --> 00:36:32.830
But sometimes we don't take notice

00:36:32.830 --> 00:36:34.430
We don't benefit from what we see

00:36:34.430 --> 00:36:35.830
We see lesson after lesson

00:36:35.830 --> 00:36:36.830
Nothing helped

00:36:36.830 --> 00:36:38.030
So Allah opens your eyes

00:36:38.030 --> 00:36:41.130
So now it will help you that you've seen something

00:36:41.130 --> 00:36:42.530
Sometimes we hear a message

00:36:42.530 --> 00:36:43.030
Powerful

00:36:43.030 --> 00:36:44.430
We know this is the truth

00:36:44.430 --> 00:36:45.830
But it doesn't strike us

00:36:45.830 --> 00:36:48.830
Because we haven't heard it with the correct ears

00:36:48.830 --> 00:36:50.530
And suddenly one day

00:36:50.530 --> 00:36:52.530
Something happens and it strikes

00:36:52.530 --> 00:36:53.930
So who opened your ears

00:36:53.930 --> 00:36:55.830
It's Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:36:55.830 --> 00:36:57.630
The same applies to our hearts

00:36:57.630 --> 00:36:59.430
Sometimes our hearts are so hardened

00:36:59.430 --> 00:37:00.730
We keep on sinning

00:37:00.730 --> 00:37:02.430
And we keep on transgressing

00:37:02.430 --> 00:37:04.930
Thinking Allah is most forgiving

00:37:04.930 --> 00:37:05.830
Most merciful

00:37:05.830 --> 00:37:07.130
Nothing changes us

00:37:07.130 --> 00:37:09.630
Until one day Allah wants to open the heart

00:37:09.630 --> 00:37:11.830
So something happens and the heart opens

00:37:11.830 --> 00:37:13.130
And suddenly we are softened

00:37:13.130 --> 00:37:14.730
By the will of Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:37:14.730 --> 00:37:16.330
Even though that particular item

00:37:16.330 --> 00:37:19.930
Might have been a point of negativity in our lives

00:37:19.930 --> 00:37:22.030
So this is a gift of Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:37:22.030 --> 00:37:24.330
Take a look at Salman al-Farisi

00:37:24.330 --> 00:37:24.830
Who was he?

00:37:25.830 --> 00:37:26.630
He was Persian

00:37:26.630 --> 00:37:28.230
He was from a noble family

00:37:28.230 --> 00:37:29.430
They used to worship the fire

00:37:29.430 --> 00:37:30.230
He refused

00:37:30.230 --> 00:37:31.430
He went away to some monks

00:37:31.430 --> 00:37:33.030
And the story is nice and long

00:37:33.030 --> 00:37:34.630
But let me make mention of

00:37:34.630 --> 00:37:36.230
The main aspect of it

00:37:36.230 --> 00:37:39.230
It is reported that he was told by one of the monks

00:37:39.230 --> 00:37:40.830
That he was with in Ammuriya

00:37:40.830 --> 00:37:42.130
Is the name of a place

00:37:42.130 --> 00:37:44.830
And he was told by this religious man

00:37:44.830 --> 00:37:46.230
That you know what

00:37:46.230 --> 00:37:48.330
I am now close to my death

00:37:48.330 --> 00:37:49.830
And I'd like to tell you

00:37:49.830 --> 00:37:51.530
That a man is going to come

00:37:51.530 --> 00:37:53.930
Who's going to preach the religion of Ibrahim

00:37:53.930 --> 00:37:54.730
What was that?

00:37:54.730 --> 00:37:56.630
Monotheism, worship one Allah

00:37:56.630 --> 00:37:59.130
One, worship your maker alone

00:37:59.130 --> 00:38:00.330
That's the beauty of Islam

00:38:00.330 --> 00:38:01.830
What makes us Muslim?

00:38:01.830 --> 00:38:04.530
We only surrender to the one who made us

00:38:04.530 --> 00:38:05.930
We never worship a person

00:38:05.930 --> 00:38:07.030
Or a stick or a stone

00:38:07.030 --> 00:38:08.130
Or a grave or a tree

00:38:08.130 --> 00:38:08.830
No

00:38:08.830 --> 00:38:11.330
The beauty of Islam lies in one thing

00:38:11.330 --> 00:38:14.330
And that is we worship our maker alone

00:38:14.330 --> 00:38:15.530
The one who made us

00:38:15.530 --> 00:38:17.630
The one whom we are going to return to

00:38:17.630 --> 00:38:18.230
That's it

00:38:18.230 --> 00:38:21.030
So there's no risk involved as Muslims

00:38:21.030 --> 00:38:22.430
When we put our heads on the ground

00:38:22.430 --> 00:38:23.230
What do we say?

00:38:23.230 --> 00:38:24.430
Oh you who made us

00:38:24.430 --> 00:38:25.930
You are the greatest

00:38:25.930 --> 00:38:27.230
Oh worshipped one

00:38:27.230 --> 00:38:28.330
You are the greatest

00:38:28.330 --> 00:38:30.630
Is there anything wrong with that statement?

00:38:30.630 --> 00:38:32.230
When we say

00:38:32.230 --> 00:38:33.830
Subhanarabbi al-A'la

00:38:33.830 --> 00:38:35.430
We are actually saying

00:38:35.430 --> 00:38:37.430
Glory be to the maker

00:38:37.430 --> 00:38:39.130
Rabbun is the one who made us

00:38:39.130 --> 00:38:41.130
And the one who is in absolute control

00:38:41.130 --> 00:38:43.730
Of every aspect of our existence

00:38:43.730 --> 00:38:45.630
You are indeed the highest

00:38:45.630 --> 00:38:46.830
What's wrong with that statement?

00:38:46.830 --> 00:38:48.130
How can people say

00:38:48.130 --> 00:38:49.130
We worship idols

00:38:49.130 --> 00:38:50.030
We worship people

00:38:50.030 --> 00:38:50.930
We worship Muhammad

00:38:50.930 --> 00:38:51.830
We worship this

00:38:51.830 --> 00:38:53.630
We worship a black box in Mecca

00:38:54.530 --> 00:38:56.030
No, that is wrong

00:38:56.030 --> 00:38:56.930
We don't

00:38:56.930 --> 00:38:59.030
We actually worship our maker alone

00:38:59.030 --> 00:39:01.630
So this was what Salman al-Farisi was told

00:39:01.630 --> 00:39:03.330
This is what intrigued them

00:39:03.330 --> 00:39:05.530
From the very beginning to this day

00:39:05.530 --> 00:39:08.030
Islam being very very fast

00:39:08.030 --> 00:39:09.430
In spreading on the globe

00:39:09.430 --> 00:39:12.030
What is it that is driving the people to Islam?

00:39:12.030 --> 00:39:13.730
It is the concept of godhood

00:39:13.730 --> 00:39:16.230
The fact that you have a direct link with your maker

00:39:16.230 --> 00:39:18.030
And you only worship your maker

00:39:18.030 --> 00:39:19.430
And none other than him

00:39:19.430 --> 00:39:20.530
Neither a messenger

00:39:20.530 --> 00:39:21.530
Nor an angel

00:39:21.530 --> 00:39:22.230
Nor a stick

00:39:22.230 --> 00:39:23.130
Nor a stone

00:39:23.130 --> 00:39:23.930
Nor an idol

00:39:23.930 --> 00:39:24.530
Nor wealth

00:39:24.530 --> 00:39:26.730
Nor anything besides your maker

00:39:26.730 --> 00:39:29.430
La ilaha illallah

00:39:29.430 --> 00:39:32.730
Muhammadun rasulullah sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:39:32.730 --> 00:39:34.230
So Salman al-Farisi

00:39:34.230 --> 00:39:35.530
When he was told that

00:39:35.530 --> 00:39:37.030
He was also told that this man

00:39:37.030 --> 00:39:39.430
Will not accept sadaqah for himself

00:39:39.430 --> 00:39:40.830
Sadaqah meaning charities

00:39:40.830 --> 00:39:41.730
He will take a gift

00:39:41.730 --> 00:39:42.830
But not a charity

00:39:42.830 --> 00:39:44.630
And he will have a mark on his back

00:39:44.630 --> 00:39:46.430
Which will be the size of a pea

00:39:46.430 --> 00:39:49.030
That will be known as the seal of prophethood

00:39:49.030 --> 00:39:51.530
And he is a person who will have good character

00:39:51.630 --> 00:39:53.330
He will call towards goodness

00:39:53.330 --> 00:39:55.030
And he will call towards

00:39:55.030 --> 00:39:57.030
Fulfilling the rights of others and so on

00:39:57.030 --> 00:39:58.830
So Salman al-Farisi says

00:39:58.830 --> 00:40:00.030
You know what?

00:40:00.030 --> 00:40:02.930
I was actually told by this particular monk

00:40:02.930 --> 00:40:04.230
That you know

00:40:04.230 --> 00:40:06.030
He will be between two deserts

00:40:06.030 --> 00:40:07.130
Where there are date palms

00:40:07.130 --> 00:40:08.930
So he went to Medina Munawwara

00:40:08.930 --> 00:40:10.430
Long story in the process

00:40:10.430 --> 00:40:11.530
He was enslaved

00:40:11.530 --> 00:40:13.230
And when he was brought to Medina Munawwara

00:40:13.230 --> 00:40:14.030
He was so happy

00:40:14.030 --> 00:40:15.130
Because he landed up

00:40:15.130 --> 00:40:16.530
Exactly where he wanted

00:40:16.530 --> 00:40:18.530
And at the time of Hijra

00:40:18.530 --> 00:40:21.030
When he saw Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:40:21.030 --> 00:40:22.230
He heard the message

00:40:22.230 --> 00:40:23.230
Correct message

00:40:23.230 --> 00:40:24.230
He was happy

00:40:24.230 --> 00:40:25.330
Then he said

00:40:25.330 --> 00:40:26.130
Let me check

00:40:26.130 --> 00:40:27.430
So he gave him something

00:40:27.430 --> 00:40:28.730
And said this is a charity

00:40:28.730 --> 00:40:29.730
So Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:40:29.730 --> 00:40:30.630
Did not take from it

00:40:30.630 --> 00:40:31.930
He gave it away

00:40:31.930 --> 00:40:33.230
And then he came the next day

00:40:33.230 --> 00:40:34.230
Or some time later

00:40:34.230 --> 00:40:35.630
And he gave a gift

00:40:35.630 --> 00:40:36.930
And he says this is not a charity

00:40:36.930 --> 00:40:37.830
It's just a gift

00:40:37.830 --> 00:40:39.230
So Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:40:39.230 --> 00:40:40.430
Partook from it

00:40:40.430 --> 00:40:41.230
Subhanallah

00:40:41.230 --> 00:40:43.230
Then he had an opportunity to see

00:40:43.230 --> 00:40:44.830
The seal of prophethood

00:40:44.830 --> 00:40:47.130
And then his heart just softened up

00:40:47.130 --> 00:40:48.630
And he bore witness

00:40:48.630 --> 00:40:50.430
La ilaha illallah

00:40:50.430 --> 00:40:53.730
Muhammadur Rasulullah sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:40:53.730 --> 00:40:55.730
The same applies to another

00:40:55.730 --> 00:40:57.730
Abdullah ibn Salam

00:40:57.730 --> 00:40:59.530
And his name according to some of the narrations

00:40:59.530 --> 00:41:00.930
Was Al-Husayn at one stage

00:41:00.930 --> 00:41:02.830
Just prior to Nabi sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:41:02.830 --> 00:41:04.730
Giving him the name Abdullah

00:41:04.730 --> 00:41:06.030
He was a Jewish rabbi

00:41:06.030 --> 00:41:08.030
He was from Banu Qaynuqa

00:41:08.030 --> 00:41:09.730
Banu Qaynuqa was one of the tribes

00:41:09.730 --> 00:41:10.730
That had come to settle

00:41:10.730 --> 00:41:12.030
Just around Medina Munawwara

00:41:12.030 --> 00:41:13.530
One of the areas there

00:41:13.530 --> 00:41:15.030
And what happened is when he came

00:41:15.030 --> 00:41:16.230
He used to teach his people

00:41:16.230 --> 00:41:18.430
And he was one of the highest of the lot

00:41:18.430 --> 00:41:20.930
And he was the leader of the Jews there

00:41:20.930 --> 00:41:22.930
The leaders of Banu Qaynuqa

00:41:22.930 --> 00:41:25.430
And when Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wa sallam came

00:41:25.430 --> 00:41:28.030
He looked, he says as we mentioned day one

00:41:28.030 --> 00:41:31.230
We said when he saw the face of Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:41:31.230 --> 00:41:33.430
He said this is not the face of a liar

00:41:33.430 --> 00:41:35.630
I can see that this man is truthful

00:41:35.630 --> 00:41:37.030
It's not the face of a liar

00:41:37.030 --> 00:41:38.830
Subhanallah

00:41:38.830 --> 00:41:40.130
So he heard the message

00:41:40.130 --> 00:41:41.730
It was a message full of peace

00:41:41.730 --> 00:41:43.630
One narration says some of the first words

00:41:43.630 --> 00:41:44.930
That were mentioned were

00:41:44.930 --> 00:41:46.030
Ayyuhannas

00:41:46.030 --> 00:41:47.130
Afshussalam

00:41:47.130 --> 00:41:48.330
Wa ata'imu al-ta'am

00:41:48.330 --> 00:41:49.430
Wasilu al-arham

00:41:49.430 --> 00:41:51.630
Wasallu bil-layli wa an-nasu niyam

00:41:51.630 --> 00:41:53.730
Tadkhulu jannata rabbikum bisalam

00:41:53.730 --> 00:41:55.230
This is according to one of the narrations

00:41:55.230 --> 00:41:56.730
That he heard the words

00:41:56.730 --> 00:41:58.330
First words, O people

00:41:58.330 --> 00:42:00.330
Spread peace, spread salam

00:42:00.330 --> 00:42:01.930
And feed the people

00:42:01.930 --> 00:42:05.230
And maintain your family relations

00:42:05.230 --> 00:42:07.130
And fulfill prayer at night

00:42:07.130 --> 00:42:08.530
When everyone is asleep

00:42:08.530 --> 00:42:11.130
And you will be able to enter paradise with ease

00:42:11.130 --> 00:42:12.330
Allahu akbar

00:42:12.330 --> 00:42:14.630
And he says when I heard that

00:42:14.630 --> 00:42:17.630
I knew that this man is actually truthful

00:42:17.730 --> 00:42:20.230
And he says he tiptoed from the back to look

00:42:20.230 --> 00:42:21.530
And to see what was happening

00:42:21.530 --> 00:42:23.830
He came forth and he declared his Shahada

00:42:23.830 --> 00:42:25.030
So Nabi sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:42:25.030 --> 00:42:26.930
Told him at that time

00:42:26.930 --> 00:42:28.030
That listen

00:42:28.030 --> 00:42:29.530
They explained to him who he was

00:42:29.530 --> 00:42:30.430
He says okay

00:42:30.430 --> 00:42:31.530
Why don't you bring your people

00:42:31.530 --> 00:42:32.930
Banu qainuqa

00:42:32.930 --> 00:42:34.030
And why don't you explain to them

00:42:34.030 --> 00:42:34.630
I'm the leader

00:42:34.630 --> 00:42:35.630
I've accepted the message

00:42:35.630 --> 00:42:37.030
It's a correct message

00:42:37.030 --> 00:42:38.430
And you people come on

00:42:38.430 --> 00:42:39.930
So he said my people

00:42:39.930 --> 00:42:40.930
I know them better

00:42:40.930 --> 00:42:42.630
They will never accept

00:42:42.630 --> 00:42:43.530
What's the reason?

00:42:43.530 --> 00:42:45.030
Because you're not from their clan

00:42:45.030 --> 00:42:46.130
You're not from them

00:42:46.130 --> 00:42:48.130
You're actually from the children of Ismail

00:42:48.130 --> 00:42:49.730
Not from the children of his haqq

00:42:49.730 --> 00:42:52.130
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala bless them all

00:42:53.130 --> 00:42:55.130
So Nabi sallallahu alayhi wa sallam said

00:42:55.130 --> 00:42:58.130
Okay why don't you just wait behind this wall

00:42:58.130 --> 00:42:59.830
There was a wall

00:42:59.830 --> 00:43:01.630
And he called Banu qainuqa

00:43:01.630 --> 00:43:02.430
Some of the leaders

00:43:02.430 --> 00:43:05.130
And he says who is this man in your midst

00:43:05.130 --> 00:43:06.830
He said oh he is a leader

00:43:06.830 --> 00:43:08.030
A son of a leader

00:43:08.030 --> 00:43:08.730
Honorable

00:43:08.730 --> 00:43:09.830
A son of an honorable

00:43:09.830 --> 00:43:10.430
Truthful

00:43:10.430 --> 00:43:11.430
Son of the truthful

00:43:11.430 --> 00:43:12.730
One of our wise men

00:43:12.730 --> 00:43:14.030
The leader from amongst us

00:43:14.030 --> 00:43:15.130
That's who he is

00:43:15.130 --> 00:43:17.930
So the prophet sallallahu alayhi wa sallam asked them

00:43:17.930 --> 00:43:18.930
What if I tell you

00:43:18.930 --> 00:43:21.130
He accepted me as the messenger

00:43:22.130 --> 00:43:23.830
They said that is impossible

00:43:23.830 --> 00:43:26.230
He can never ever do that

00:43:26.230 --> 00:43:26.730
Not you

00:43:26.730 --> 00:43:27.530
No ways

00:43:27.530 --> 00:43:28.630
It can't happen

00:43:28.630 --> 00:43:31.330
So Nabi sallallahu alayhi wa sallam called him from behind

00:43:31.330 --> 00:43:32.930
And says come come forth

00:43:32.930 --> 00:43:34.330
So when he came forth

00:43:34.330 --> 00:43:34.730
He says

00:43:34.730 --> 00:43:35.830
Ya rasulallah

00:43:35.830 --> 00:43:38.430
Inni ash hadu alla ilaha illallah

00:43:38.430 --> 00:43:41.230
Wa ash hadu annaka abduhu wa rasuluhu

00:43:41.230 --> 00:43:42.730
You know what they said

00:43:42.730 --> 00:43:43.630
Immediately they said

00:43:43.630 --> 00:43:44.630
Oh he's a cheat

00:43:44.630 --> 00:43:46.030
And his father was a cheat

00:43:46.030 --> 00:43:47.330
He's the lowest from amongst us

00:43:47.330 --> 00:43:48.530
And so was his father

00:43:48.530 --> 00:43:49.530
And he is a traitor

00:43:49.530 --> 00:43:50.730
And so was his father

00:43:50.730 --> 00:43:51.930
And he has deceived us

00:43:51.930 --> 00:43:52.730
And so did his dad

00:43:52.730 --> 00:43:53.630
And they went away

00:43:53.630 --> 00:43:54.530
Allahu akbar

00:43:54.530 --> 00:43:55.730
Look at this

00:43:55.730 --> 00:43:57.230
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:43:57.230 --> 00:43:59.030
Not make our hearts hard

00:43:59.030 --> 00:44:00.730
The lesson we learn from that

00:44:00.730 --> 00:44:02.730
Allah shows us signs in our lives

00:44:02.730 --> 00:44:03.530
To leave sin

00:44:03.530 --> 00:44:04.230
To turn to him

00:44:04.230 --> 00:44:05.230
To read salah

00:44:05.230 --> 00:44:06.130
To fight laziness

00:44:06.130 --> 00:44:09.030
When it comes to obedience of Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:44:09.030 --> 00:44:10.230
Not to please shaytan

00:44:10.230 --> 00:44:11.430
To try our best

00:44:11.430 --> 00:44:12.330
To turn in tawbah

00:44:12.330 --> 00:44:13.530
But sometimes we don't turn

00:44:13.530 --> 00:44:15.030
We continue in our sin

00:44:15.030 --> 00:44:17.230
And if you really study the sin

00:44:17.230 --> 00:44:18.730
Wallahi it's worth nothing

00:44:18.730 --> 00:44:20.730
It's worth nothing at all

00:44:20.730 --> 00:44:22.130
What did we achieve by it?

00:44:22.130 --> 00:44:23.830
There is much more sweetness

00:44:23.830 --> 00:44:25.430
In the obedience of Allah

00:44:25.430 --> 00:44:28.730
Than there is in engaging in any sin ever

00:44:28.730 --> 00:44:29.730
Believe me

00:44:29.730 --> 00:44:30.830
The sins

00:44:30.830 --> 00:44:32.630
All they can be is

00:44:32.630 --> 00:44:33.830
For a moment or two

00:44:33.830 --> 00:44:34.930
A little bit of pleasure

00:44:34.930 --> 00:44:36.330
After that there is regret

00:44:36.330 --> 00:44:37.330
On top of it regret

00:44:37.330 --> 00:44:38.430
On top of it shame

00:44:38.430 --> 00:44:39.430
On top of it

00:44:39.430 --> 00:44:41.130
Perhaps even a person

00:44:41.130 --> 00:44:43.230
May be belittled in front of society

00:44:43.230 --> 00:44:44.130
And community

00:44:44.130 --> 00:44:46.230
And they may not know where to hide their face

00:44:46.230 --> 00:44:49.830
Only because they displeased Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:44:49.830 --> 00:44:50.930
But that cannot happen

00:44:50.930 --> 00:44:53.430
When we obey the commands of Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:44:53.430 --> 00:44:55.830
So these are some of the statements

00:44:55.830 --> 00:44:58.230
That were coming from the people

00:44:58.230 --> 00:45:02.530
In fact there is a man known as Abu Tayhan

00:45:02.530 --> 00:45:05.030
And he too he makes mention

00:45:05.030 --> 00:45:06.630
He came from Al-Sham

00:45:06.630 --> 00:45:08.230
The region in the north

00:45:08.230 --> 00:45:11.630
And he came down to this area in Arabia

00:45:11.630 --> 00:45:12.630
Madina Munawwara

00:45:12.630 --> 00:45:14.930
He lived with Banu Qurayba

00:45:14.930 --> 00:45:16.330
And what happened?

00:45:16.330 --> 00:45:18.330
On his deathbed he tells Banu Qurayba

00:45:18.330 --> 00:45:21.130
Do you know why I left the land

00:45:21.130 --> 00:45:22.330
Which is so rich

00:45:22.330 --> 00:45:23.930
And so full of food and drink

00:45:23.930 --> 00:45:25.130
And I came to the land

00:45:25.130 --> 00:45:28.230
That is full of hunger

00:45:28.230 --> 00:45:29.930
Meaning Hijaz

00:45:29.930 --> 00:45:31.130
And I have come to this land

00:45:31.130 --> 00:45:32.830
Where there is nothing

00:45:32.830 --> 00:45:34.530
They said well you know better

00:45:34.530 --> 00:45:36.330
He says because there is a messenger

00:45:36.330 --> 00:45:37.830
Who is going to come in this land

00:45:37.830 --> 00:45:40.030
According to the Bible and the Torah

00:45:40.030 --> 00:45:41.130
And according to the books

00:45:41.130 --> 00:45:42.930
This is the land is going to come in

00:45:42.930 --> 00:45:45.430
So I am here waiting for him

00:45:45.430 --> 00:45:46.630
Sadly what happened?

00:45:46.630 --> 00:45:48.030
He passed away

00:45:48.030 --> 00:45:49.930
He passed away before

00:45:49.930 --> 00:45:52.730
The sending of Nabi صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:45:52.730 --> 00:45:53.730
As a messenger

00:45:53.730 --> 00:45:56.630
Then another piece of evidence to prove

00:45:56.630 --> 00:45:59.630
That the world was waiting for this man

00:45:59.630 --> 00:46:02.030
Heraclius

00:46:02.030 --> 00:46:03.930
What happened?

00:46:03.930 --> 00:46:09.830
When Quraysh had sent their team to him

00:46:09.830 --> 00:46:12.030
They asked, he asked them the question

00:46:12.030 --> 00:46:14.130
This man who is claiming to be a messenger

00:46:14.130 --> 00:46:15.530
Who is he, what is he and so on

00:46:15.530 --> 00:46:18.130
So many questions and Abu Sufyan was responding

00:46:18.130 --> 00:46:20.630
And Abu Sufyan gave one response after another

00:46:20.630 --> 00:46:22.730
The point being raised is at the end

00:46:22.730 --> 00:46:26.140
Heraclius says

00:46:26.140 --> 00:46:28.940
Yes we have been waiting for this man

00:46:28.940 --> 00:46:31.840
But I did not expect him to come from amongst you

00:46:31.840 --> 00:46:33.040
Same thing

00:46:33.040 --> 00:46:35.540
Look at how this thing comes

00:46:35.540 --> 00:46:37.140
From person to person where

00:46:37.140 --> 00:46:38.540
Because it's not from us

00:46:38.540 --> 00:46:39.740
Now we don't want it

00:46:39.740 --> 00:46:40.840
It's someone else

00:46:40.840 --> 00:46:42.240
This person is a different tribe

00:46:42.240 --> 00:46:43.140
A different clan

00:46:43.140 --> 00:46:44.440
They come from a different area

00:46:44.440 --> 00:46:45.340
Different continent

00:46:45.340 --> 00:46:46.240
Different color

00:46:46.240 --> 00:46:47.640
So we don't want to accept

00:46:47.640 --> 00:46:48.940
That is ignorance

00:46:48.940 --> 00:46:51.940
That will keep people away from what is right

00:46:51.940 --> 00:46:52.540
Remember that

00:46:52.540 --> 00:46:54.440
It did the same at that time

00:46:54.440 --> 00:46:56.340
And it repeats itself even now

00:46:56.340 --> 00:46:58.140
May Allah سبحانه وتعالى

00:46:58.140 --> 00:46:59.640
Bless us all

00:46:59.640 --> 00:47:02.040
So this was something very very important

00:47:02.040 --> 00:47:04.240
Another man who also

00:47:04.240 --> 00:47:06.140
Spoke very highly

00:47:06.140 --> 00:47:07.440
But Allah سبحانه وتعالى

00:47:07.440 --> 00:47:09.840
Did not intend for him to accept Islam

00:47:09.840 --> 00:47:12.440
His name was Umayyah ibn Abi Salth

00:47:12.440 --> 00:47:13.740
He was a poet

00:47:13.740 --> 00:47:15.440
He was a top brain

00:47:15.440 --> 00:47:16.240
Very intelligent

00:47:16.240 --> 00:47:18.140
He did not worship the idols

00:47:18.140 --> 00:47:19.440
And he did not drink

00:47:19.440 --> 00:47:20.540
He prohibited it

00:47:20.540 --> 00:47:21.540
And he used to worship

00:47:21.540 --> 00:47:23.840
According to the worship of Ibrahim عليه السلام

00:47:23.840 --> 00:47:25.140
One God alone

00:47:25.140 --> 00:47:26.140
And he had read

00:47:26.140 --> 00:47:28.840
He was one of the literate from amongst Quraysh

00:47:28.840 --> 00:47:29.240
Literate

00:47:29.240 --> 00:47:29.940
He could read

00:47:29.940 --> 00:47:30.640
Thaqif

00:47:30.640 --> 00:47:32.340
He came from Taif in fact

00:47:32.340 --> 00:47:33.940
He was a Thaqafi

00:47:33.940 --> 00:47:35.340
And what happened is

00:47:35.340 --> 00:47:38.640
His poetry was taken by the Arabs at large

00:47:38.640 --> 00:47:40.440
One of the most eloquent people

00:47:40.440 --> 00:47:42.340
So much so Nabi صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:47:42.340 --> 00:47:43.640
Used to enjoy

00:47:43.640 --> 00:47:45.740
Later on after Nubuwa

00:47:45.740 --> 00:47:48.840
Listening to the poetry of Umayyah ibn Abi Salth

00:47:48.840 --> 00:47:50.440
And one day the Prophet صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:47:50.440 --> 00:47:52.140
Heard 100 couplets

00:47:52.140 --> 00:47:52.740
And he says

00:47:52.740 --> 00:47:54.740
In kaada layuslim

00:47:54.740 --> 00:47:57.540
This man was about to be a Muslim

00:47:57.540 --> 00:47:59.040
So what stopped him

00:47:59.040 --> 00:48:00.340
Well, he read the books

00:48:00.340 --> 00:48:01.540
And he knew there is a messenger

00:48:01.540 --> 00:48:02.740
Coming from this area

00:48:02.740 --> 00:48:03.740
He was excited

00:48:03.740 --> 00:48:05.040
He was hoping it would be him

00:48:05.040 --> 00:48:07.340
Because he was very pious

00:48:07.340 --> 00:48:08.840
So when the messenger came

00:48:08.840 --> 00:48:09.540
He rejected

00:48:09.540 --> 00:48:10.140
Why

00:48:10.140 --> 00:48:11.240
He was jealous

00:48:11.240 --> 00:48:12.840
Look at what jealousy does

00:48:12.840 --> 00:48:14.340
And he died on that condition

00:48:14.340 --> 00:48:15.040
Imagine

00:48:15.040 --> 00:48:17.040
And yet he was a person who

00:48:17.040 --> 00:48:18.540
All he had to do was now

00:48:18.540 --> 00:48:20.440
Believe in Muhammad Rasulullah

00:48:20.440 --> 00:48:21.240
Because he had the

00:48:21.240 --> 00:48:23.340
La ilaha illallah in him already

00:48:23.340 --> 00:48:24.640
But he missed the other half

00:48:24.640 --> 00:48:25.740
So what happened to him

00:48:25.740 --> 00:48:27.240
He died as a disbeliever

00:48:27.240 --> 00:48:28.540
May Allah سبحانه وتعالى

00:48:28.540 --> 00:48:30.040
Safeguard us

00:48:30.040 --> 00:48:31.540
This is what jealousy does

00:48:31.540 --> 00:48:32.540
When we become jealous

00:48:32.540 --> 00:48:34.040
That the Dean has come one side

00:48:34.040 --> 00:48:35.040
And not here

00:48:35.040 --> 00:48:36.040
Then we can lose from it

00:48:36.040 --> 00:48:38.040
So let's not let that overtake us ever

00:48:38.040 --> 00:48:39.340
May Allah سبحانه وتعالى

00:48:39.340 --> 00:48:40.340
Open our doors

00:48:40.340 --> 00:48:42.340
And grant us goodness

00:48:42.340 --> 00:48:43.440
Yesterday I made mention

00:48:43.440 --> 00:48:44.640
Of a very interesting point

00:48:44.640 --> 00:48:46.140
One of the signs of nubuwa

00:48:46.140 --> 00:48:47.940
Now we are moving closer to

00:48:47.940 --> 00:48:49.940
The time when the angel came in

00:48:49.940 --> 00:48:50.940
We would find

00:48:50.940 --> 00:48:53.240
Rasulullah صلى الله عليه وسلم says

00:48:53.240 --> 00:48:55.640
When I was in Makkah al-Mukarrama

00:48:55.640 --> 00:48:57.140
I know a stone

00:48:57.140 --> 00:48:59.540
That used to make salam to me

00:48:59.540 --> 00:49:00.340
Imagine

00:49:00.340 --> 00:49:01.940
And you know what he says

00:49:01.940 --> 00:49:03.340
He says it later on in this hadith

00:49:03.340 --> 00:49:04.840
It is reported by Jabir ibn Samullah

00:49:04.840 --> 00:49:06.040
In Sahih Muslim

00:49:06.040 --> 00:49:08.240
He says I know the stone up to now

00:49:08.240 --> 00:49:09.640
I know which stone it is

00:49:09.640 --> 00:49:10.740
Subhanallah

00:49:10.740 --> 00:49:11.740
Amazing

00:49:11.740 --> 00:49:13.040
And some other narration say

00:49:13.040 --> 00:49:14.340
Not only that stone

00:49:14.340 --> 00:49:15.540
But several other stones

00:49:15.540 --> 00:49:16.440
Now someone might think

00:49:16.440 --> 00:49:18.840
How can a stone make salam

00:49:18.840 --> 00:49:19.540
To the messenger

00:49:19.540 --> 00:49:21.940
Well look at Musa عليه السلام

00:49:21.940 --> 00:49:23.440
Didn't he have a stick

00:49:23.440 --> 00:49:24.040
That could actually

00:49:24.040 --> 00:49:25.340
That actually ate up

00:49:25.340 --> 00:49:26.840
All the other serpents

00:49:26.840 --> 00:49:28.140
Of those magicians

00:49:28.140 --> 00:49:29.940
What about Sulaiman عليه السلام

00:49:29.940 --> 00:49:31.440
Couldn't he speak to the wind

00:49:31.440 --> 00:49:32.440
And the other creatures

00:49:32.540 --> 00:49:33.740
So this was a messenger

00:49:33.740 --> 00:49:35.340
The highest of all messengers

00:49:35.340 --> 00:49:36.840
Nothing strange about

00:49:36.840 --> 00:49:38.440
A rock making salam to him

00:49:38.440 --> 00:49:40.740
These creatures knew who he was

00:49:40.740 --> 00:49:41.740
Subhanallah

00:49:41.740 --> 00:49:44.040
They knew exactly who he was

00:49:44.040 --> 00:49:45.040
Look at the cloud

00:49:45.040 --> 00:49:46.940
Refusing to let the sun harm

00:49:46.940 --> 00:49:49.240
Yet he wasn't even a Nabi at the time

00:49:49.240 --> 00:49:50.440
Subhanallah

00:49:50.440 --> 00:49:52.240
And this is authentic

00:49:52.240 --> 00:49:54.940
May Allah سبحانه وتعالى bless us

00:49:54.940 --> 00:49:56.740
May He grant us goodness

00:49:56.740 --> 00:49:59.040
صلى الله وسلم وبارك عليه

00:49:59.040 --> 00:50:01.140
وعلى آله وأصحابه أجمعين

00:50:01.140 --> 00:50:03.640
This is Nabi صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:50:03.640 --> 00:50:05.740
So what had happened is

00:50:05.740 --> 00:50:07.240
Nabi صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:50:07.240 --> 00:50:10.140
Sent letters at one stage later on

00:50:10.140 --> 00:50:11.340
To all the leaders around

00:50:11.340 --> 00:50:12.940
I'm sure we know that

00:50:12.940 --> 00:50:15.140
Well how did they treat the letters

00:50:15.140 --> 00:50:16.440
How they treated the letters

00:50:16.440 --> 00:50:18.240
Already proves that they knew

00:50:18.240 --> 00:50:20.240
There is a messenger coming

00:50:20.240 --> 00:50:23.040
Because Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:50:23.040 --> 00:50:25.540
Was no force to be reckoned with at the time

00:50:25.540 --> 00:50:27.240
He didn't have a military might

00:50:27.240 --> 00:50:29.140
But it was a spiritual might

00:50:29.140 --> 00:50:31.440
So these big big armies of the Romans

00:50:31.440 --> 00:50:32.140
And the others

00:50:32.140 --> 00:50:33.840
They could have walked straight through

00:50:33.840 --> 00:50:36.240
And dealt a heavy blow to those people

00:50:36.240 --> 00:50:37.240
But what happened

00:50:37.240 --> 00:50:41.340
All of them received the messengers very well

00:50:41.340 --> 00:50:42.840
And some of them accepted

00:50:42.840 --> 00:50:44.240
Some of them did not

00:50:44.240 --> 00:50:45.340
And those who did not

00:50:45.340 --> 00:50:46.740
Did not dishonor the messengers

00:50:46.740 --> 00:50:47.740
Besides one man

00:50:47.740 --> 00:50:48.540
Who was that?

00:50:48.540 --> 00:50:49.340
Kisra

00:50:49.340 --> 00:50:50.440
Why Kisra?

00:50:50.440 --> 00:50:52.540
The fire worshipper in Iran

00:50:52.540 --> 00:50:53.740
What is the reason?

00:50:53.740 --> 00:50:54.840
The reason is

00:50:54.840 --> 00:50:56.840
He had no knowledge of the previous books

00:50:56.840 --> 00:50:58.440
They used to worship fire

00:50:58.440 --> 00:50:59.940
Whereas the Jews and the Christians

00:50:59.940 --> 00:51:01.240
They had knowledge of the book

00:51:01.240 --> 00:51:02.940
So they all honored the messengers

00:51:02.940 --> 00:51:04.040
Sent the messengers back

00:51:04.040 --> 00:51:05.740
With gifts in most cases

00:51:05.740 --> 00:51:07.840
And as for Najashi

00:51:07.840 --> 00:51:10.040
The Negus of Abyssinia

00:51:10.040 --> 00:51:11.940
He accepted the message

00:51:11.940 --> 00:51:13.740
Almost instantaneously

00:51:13.740 --> 00:51:15.140
Subhanallah

00:51:15.140 --> 00:51:16.340
May Allah سبحانه وتعالى

00:51:16.340 --> 00:51:17.840
Help us accept this message

00:51:17.840 --> 00:51:19.940
Nabi صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:51:19.940 --> 00:51:21.040
At one stage

00:51:21.040 --> 00:51:23.840
Started seeing dreams

00:51:23.840 --> 00:51:25.440
And these dreams

00:51:25.440 --> 00:51:26.840
He would see them at night

00:51:26.840 --> 00:51:27.540
And in the morning

00:51:27.540 --> 00:51:28.740
They would come true

00:51:28.740 --> 00:51:31.140
As though he is reliving it

00:51:31.140 --> 00:51:33.540
This was the first signs of Nubuwa

00:51:33.540 --> 00:51:35.440
Just as he was about to get profited

00:51:35.440 --> 00:51:36.440
By the age of 40

00:51:36.440 --> 00:51:37.740
This started happening

00:51:37.740 --> 00:51:39.440
Where he would see dreams

00:51:39.440 --> 00:51:40.140
And the next day

00:51:40.140 --> 00:51:40.740
It would happen

00:51:40.740 --> 00:51:41.540
It would come

00:51:41.540 --> 00:51:42.240
Dream again

00:51:42.240 --> 00:51:42.940
It would come true

00:51:42.940 --> 00:51:43.540
Dream again

00:51:43.540 --> 00:51:44.440
It would come true

00:51:44.440 --> 00:51:45.540
Subhanallah

00:51:45.540 --> 00:51:47.540
And this led him

00:51:47.540 --> 00:51:49.840
To secluding himself

00:51:49.840 --> 00:51:51.640
So he drove himself away

00:51:51.640 --> 00:51:52.540
And he used to go

00:51:52.540 --> 00:51:55.140
Northwest of Mecca

00:51:55.140 --> 00:51:56.840
A place known as Hira

00:51:56.840 --> 00:51:59.140
It was a little cave in a mount

00:51:59.140 --> 00:52:00.940
And he used to go there

00:52:00.940 --> 00:52:02.440
And sit and meditate

00:52:02.440 --> 00:52:03.840
And Inshallah tomorrow

00:52:03.840 --> 00:52:04.940
We will see what happened

00:52:04.940 --> 00:52:05.840
Inshallah

00:52:05.840 --> 00:52:07.240
As he was meditating

00:52:07.240 --> 00:52:09.040
What was he meditating over

00:52:09.040 --> 00:52:10.440
What exactly happened

00:52:10.440 --> 00:52:11.540
And as a result

00:52:11.540 --> 00:52:12.840
May Allah سبحانه وتعالى

00:52:12.840 --> 00:52:13.840
Bless us all

00:52:13.840 --> 00:52:16.140
It was the blessing of Allah

00:52:16.140 --> 00:52:17.740
Upon not only Quraysh

00:52:17.740 --> 00:52:19.440
But humanity at large

00:52:19.440 --> 00:52:20.540
Not only humanity

00:52:20.540 --> 00:52:23.240
But the entire existence was blessed

00:52:23.240 --> 00:52:25.040
By what happened in that grave

00:52:25.040 --> 00:52:25.640
I'm sorry

00:52:25.640 --> 00:52:26.540
In that cave

00:52:26.540 --> 00:52:27.840
May Allah سبحانه وتعالى

00:52:27.840 --> 00:52:28.540
Bless us

00:52:28.540 --> 00:52:30.040
May he make us understand

00:52:30.040 --> 00:52:31.640
And realize this blessing

00:52:31.640 --> 00:52:33.240
And may he make us embrace it

00:52:33.240 --> 00:52:34.340
Until we meet again tomorrow

00:52:34.340 --> 00:52:35.040
Inshallah

00:52:35.040 --> 00:52:35.440
We say

00:52:35.440 --> 00:52:37.940
وَصَلَى اللَّهُ وَسَلَّمَ وَبَارَكَ عَلَى نَبِينَ مُحَمَّدٍ

00:52:37.940 --> 00:52:38.640
Subhanallah

00:52:38.640 --> 00:52:39.040
بِحَمْدِهِ

00:52:39.040 --> 00:52:40.540
سُبْحَانَكَ اللَّهُم وَبِحَمْدِكِ

00:52:40.540 --> 00:52:42.440
أَشْهَدُ أَلَّا إِلَهَ إِلَّا أَنْتَ نَسْتَغْفِرُكَ

00:52:42.440 --> 00:52:43.240
وَنَتُوبُوا إِلَيْكِ
